Knowledge is one the most valuable assets in todays companies .
Artificial Intelligence ( AI ) techniques aim to represent the knowledge in a way that can be applied to solving complex problems or supporting decision making processes .
This paper presents SABUMO , a framework based on ontologies that allows experts to represent and share their knowledge with other experts by means of shared and controlled vocabularies .
The power of knowledge is a very important resource for preserving valuable heritage , learning new things , solving problems , creating core competences , and initiating new situations for both individuals and organizations today and in the future ( Liao , 2003 ) .

